    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 38,648₽ | 物品价值: 2,162 | Ragman报价: 1,340₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 43,242₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级1 < GP x8 | Σ ≈ 60,000₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级1 < 47,134₽\n\n任务需要 x1 > RUAF Infiltrator - Part 2 @ 莲花\n\nKora-Kulon防弹衣是一款适合长期穿着的防弹衣，适用于内务部和国防部人员的所有行动。这款防弹衣的设计使得它可以作为外套的打底，保护穿戴者抵御枪械和刀具的攻击。数字迷彩版本。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 38,648₽ | 物品价值: 2,162 | Ragman报价: 1,340₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 43,242₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级1 < GP x8 | Σ ≈ 60,000₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级1 < 47,134₽\n\n任务需要 x1 > RUAF Infiltrator - Part 2 @ 莲花\n\nThe Kora-Kulon bulletproof vest is a means of individual armor protection of long-term wear, allowing to perform all types of professional activities of the personnel of the Ministry of Internal Affairs and Ministry of Defense units. The design of the bulletproof vest allows its use in concealed operation under outer clothing. Designed to protect the wearer from firearms and sharp weapons. EMR (Digital Flora) camouflage version."
    },
